    "The mainstream technologies used in traditional classification methods were Hidden Markov Models (HMM) and Support Vector Machines (SVM).",
    "In comparison, the cost of recognition at this stage is relatively high, while the accuracy of recognition is relatively low.",
    "In the past ten years, there has been a proliferation of high-tech and new technologies for sign language recognition.",
